summary: This is a custom voice set of a male Dremora for ChizFoShiz's Voiceset mod.
descriptionHtml:
There is no point in trying to contact me as all I do is log on once in a great while and drop off things I made.
I also made a female child voiceset.

-NEEDS VOICESET MOD, check it out!-
VOICESET MOD http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51387/?tab=2&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fajax%2Fmodfiles%2F%3Fid%3D51387&pUp=1

Makes you sound like a bloodthirsty male Dremora! A voicepack for ChizFoShiz's Voiceset mod.
I am mainly just dropping this off, there will be little to updates, unless it's something major. You
are free to edit and reupload without my permission. (I would be grateful if you put a link to your version as a comment on this one though! <3 It would be easier for others to find)

There is little to no chance for a female Dremora voiceset, as there is no female Dremora sounds in Skyrim. There could be, but that would require editing fof the existing voices, and I am not going to be the one to do that.
author: pwnlink3
